When uploading an attachment that's too large, the error reports the file size in MB units, but the value is actually in MiB units. This is confusing on modern operating systems that use the MB unit correctly.

This is probably a wide spread problem across JIRA. Hopefully the code is centralised and it can be fixed everywhere in one fell swoop.
